            <span class="note"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2l3 6.6 7 .8-5.2 4.8L18.3 21 12 17.4 5.7 21l1.5-6.8L2 9.4l7-.8z" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/></svg>4,9</span><span>(178 avis)</span>
            <span><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 21c4.5-4 7-7.6 7-11a7 7 0 1 0-14 0c0 3.4 2.5 7 7 11z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2.6"/></svg>Lyon 7e · 3,9 km</span>
          </p>
          <p class="resultat-artisan__desc">A remplacé votre tableau électrique en janvier. Certifiés Qualifelec, diagnostic gratuit.</p>
          <div class="resultat-artisan__tags"><span class="chip">Mise aux normes</span><span class="chip">Tableau</span><span class="chip">Domotique</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="resultat-artisan__fin">
